# The modern version of that system, [[Systeme Internationale d'Unites]] ([[International System of Units]]), or [[SI]] system of measurements that is based on the [[base unit]]s of the [[meter]]/[[metre]], the [[kilogram]], the [[second]], the [[ampere]], the [[kelvin]], the [[mole]], and the [[candela]].
#: see [[Appendix:SI_units|Appendix on SI Units]]
# Any variant of that system, that was not codified as SI, such as [[cgs]]

